REMINDER: Toast 5.2 Update Now Available!

In case you missed it, the Toast 5.2 update is now available for FREE download at:*

http://roxio.chtah.com/a/tA$He5NAHsqQEALrCLPAHvX6bO7/rmac5

Great new features and improvements include:
*Mac OS 10.2 Support: Compatibility with the latest OS from Apple.
*Support for 52x recorders: Now get the most out of your hardware
with Toast!
*CD-Text Support: Toast 5.2 now writes CD-Text information for album
name and track information to recorded audio discs. This information
is viewable in CD audio players that display CD-Text. Note that not
all recorders support burning CD-Text, so check with your manufacturer
if in doubt.
*Enhanced VideoCD QuickTime Codec: The Toast VideoCD codec has been
enhanced to support multiple G4 processors, speeding the encoding
process. It also offers more accurate preservation of color and
contrast.
*Enhanced Quartz text rendering for improved interface usability.

The update is FREE via download to all registered users of Toast 5
Titanium.* If you have a dial-up connection, and have trouble
downloading the update files, you can also order them on CD for
the cost of shipping and handling: $15.95. Go here to order:

http://roxio.chtah.com/a/tA$He5NAHsqQEALrCLPAHvX6bO7/rmac6

Or, if you don't yet have Toast 5 Titanium, now's the time to
upgrade! Check out our great offers here:
http://roxio.chtah.com/a/tA$He5NAHsqQEALrCLPAHvX6bO7/rmac1

*System requirements are Mac OS 9.1 or later, or Mac OS X version
10.1.2 or later. Please note that the updates will NOT install on
a machine where Toast 5 Titanium is not present.

